  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-499b0046-d6ba-496c-934b-26e7453749fa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ff6fed24-e846-4984-8bc0-beb97c415843\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-00a420ec-8cda-4439-bd32-61292b24266c\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 31</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bc00c813-0be7-4c3c-8fe6-2a6fd1a0047d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e4679605-2f68-4b27-8262-a55cc1c6d370\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9d24a6d1-f97a-4bf5-b146-94b1476d708b\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-663c98d8-e2fd-44ac-b8be-964acc460ae2\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[본격적인 스토리보딩 작업]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3e85bf0c-dbe0-4298-a730-348e1f788d58\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-027cba1c-eab5-4ea3-8074-bc5869646094\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 스토리보딩 작업에 들어갑니다. 지금까지는 자료나 개념에 대해 심도있게 생각했습니다. 물론 아직은 미흡한 부분이나 보강해야하는 사항이 있지만 앞으로 채워나가도록 하겠습니다. 이제부터는 하나하나 PPT 파일을 정리하도록 하겠습니다. 이제 시작입니다. 약 두달 뒤 나름 완벽한 (주)파파스컴퍼니 기획문서가 완성되기를 희망해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-393ebd14-c635-47f8-8d64-be2e407d0dba\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c9caacf-10a6-4582-a33c-46291f449d38\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f8b7090d-7c17-4f16-ad0e-cd818d7a4e41\" style=\"color:#686868;\"><b>너무 소심하고 까다롭게 자신의 행동을 고민하지 말라 . 모든 인생은 실험이다 . 더많이 실험할수록 더나아진다 </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-cite\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-96a12feb-85ce-46d7-8524-47668fc7fd37\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f59c8032-81ff-46aa-9f48-e911d9613a35\" style=\"\">랄프 왈도 에머슨</span></p></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9ce1327b-4d99-4e7f-86e5-ea0dc118551c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-903777f0-9890-47f5-b445-749ccae5316e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d0a217b0-3682-4ad9-84ee-771025585e54\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-54ac836a-38a3-41a4-bc16-159405735de1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:709px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-54ac836a-38a3-41a4-bc16-159405735de1\", \"src\" : \"https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTdfOCAg/MDAxNjY2MDE2ODQxNzAw.MFPetfRtOqhnhNPL2ZtpwJQPxy3mIHC